metadata.name: YIN YANG
metadata.description:
Discovering the polarities in ourselves and are triggered in communication or just contact with the other. We often judge too quickly. In order to make our awareness beter work, we can use the yin-yang mouvement in order to get out of the deadlock.
I am looking for a 3D animation artist in order to make this 2007 design alive. We can create a split for that new work!
